===Get closer to Cocolia's echo{{subst:void|<!--101130124-->}}===
{{Mission Description|type=trailblaze|location=Corridor of Fading Echoes|update|The echoing mirage of the Supreme Guardian has appeared in front of you once again &mdash; however, this time, the guardian's noble daughter is no longer by her side.<br />Although this place has been devoured by the Fragmentum to its core and nothing is behaving the way it should, this is something even more peculiar...<br />Is this a sign of misfortune? Or could it just be one error out of the tens of thousands taking place in the Fragmentum? The answer to this question lies in the echoing cadence of the humanoid.}}
